{"tid":744428,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖多字多災多難] 石垣島 (加外島) 8日7夜 深度自駕遊","createTime":"2018-07-16T02:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T02:37:25.000Z","uid":113944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fdeae722b97874d233f11a9b49324390bfe50105","tid":744428,"uid":113944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T02:37:25.000Z","msg":"終於黎到夏天梗係要去享受下陽光與海灘 , <br />\n去得8日咁多, 想唔深度遊都幾難, <br />\n加上仲有同女朋友一齊左咁耐都未試過 2 個人去旅行 , <br />\n所以預左第1日開始就因為天氣太熱/搵唔到路/唔知食咩好開始鬧交到返香港<br />\n<br />\n所以plan左行程如下:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 - 渣車 hea 遊<br />\nDay 2 - 渣車 hea 遊<br />\nDay 3 - 渣車 hea 遊<br />\nDay 4 - 渣車 hea 遊<br />\nDay 5 - 渣車 hea 遊<br />\nDay 6 - 渣車 hea 遊<br />\nDay 7 - 渣車 hea 遊<br />\nDay 8 - 返香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為plan黎都徙鳩氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/zLmLd3aZwfzhqQ0p-bepksqp-DRcnTDWgvszQZvdIsL-48vGVo-WLeutlo9K2ag0FkT0IcRlqX-KKEQ1iPYz=w1600-h767-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh6.googleusercontent.com%2FzLmLd3aZwfzhqQ0p-bepksqp-DRcnTDWgvszQZvdIsL-48vGVo-WLeutlo9K2ag0FkT0IcRlqX-KKEQ1iPYz%3Dw1600-h767-rw&h=4e32246c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7點40分機 晨咁早大小姐脾氣已經唔係咁好 , <br />\n加上搭 N 車太多人 , 坐都冇得坐企足成粒鐘<br />\n所以都係唔敢點撩佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出發時侯香港天氣都唔錯, 有 D 雲加少少陽光 , <br />\n加上沖繩果邊岩岩打完風，到時天氣都應該會唔錯<br />\n但唔好意思第一日落機太累真係冇咩點影相，俾住張酒店相大家睇睇先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/Ny348Tyk0WW_ZwWD_YyEeN1CpfWZ8HtmXAPCCtspDRSRtbEZoPcZ4y6KPR31EanXfU8IIjIOAQJAylSrvlgy=w1600-h767-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh4.googleusercontent.com%2FNy348Tyk0WW_ZwWD_YyEeN1CpfWZ8HtmXAPCCtspDRSRtbEZoPcZ4y6KPR31EanXfU8IIjIOAQJAylSrvlgy%3Dw1600-h767-rw&h=a3695182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/GPqEMXu_RN-iR5KOrfHkIpPjOrbJq7aZte-k2sMCxMSXqK4CQFIgR-EH6Q3zmbjzMd5e7qIFDLE_uCEr4f2C=w1600-h767-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh5.googleusercontent.com%2FGPqEMXu_RN-iR5KOrfHkIpPjOrbJq7aZte-k2sMCxMSXqK4CQFIgR-EH6Q3zmbjzMd5e7qIFDLE_uCEr4f2C%3Dw1600-h767-rw&h=1dbe4fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n間房都幾闊落，望出窗就已經係泳池，算係比想像中好好多<br />\n<br />\n可以推薦俾大家 , 間酒店叫做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港機場富豪酒店 ................"}]}